                    },
                    "body": "I can see the utility of such a function, but I'm not sure why this function would be located in Zend_Loader. Ralph, do you know? If not, maybe Alex or Matthew can give us some historical perspective. Please evaluate and categorize as needed.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wil",
