                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/34716",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ralph",
                        "name": "ralph",
                        "displayName": "Ralph Schindler",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Since ZF doesnt support 5.2.1 (or lower) and since this function in php:\n\nhttp:\/\/us2.php.net\/manual\/en\/function.sys-get-temp-dir.php\n\nhas been in place since that version, it makes sense to use that function instead of a userland function such as this.\n\nFeel free to reopen if I am missing something.\n-ralph",
